{"tid":1326103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小弟同一班文字人整咗本關於反送中嘅小冊子喺會展派","createTime":"2019-07-17T05:52:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T10:09:48.000Z","uid":3904,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"30610ab7fd2c701532e938fab20f519022612c45","tid":1326103,"uid":3904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T05:52:46.000Z","msg":"好耐冇上過嚟，雖然之前退出咗連登，但今次真係要上嚟講兩句。<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，小弟同一班文字人整咗本關於反送中嘅小冊子喺書展派，有興趣嘅可以過嚟拎本。<br />\n<br />\n呢本書除咗之前喺連登嘅徵文，仲包括小弟訪問前線死士嘅紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n現場會有六個booth派呢本書，小弟都勇武一次企正喺三中商門口派（雖然係咁俾廢老屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n希望呢幾日會嚟書展嘅巴絲打可以支持吓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UvZ90dE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUvZ90dE.jpg&h=616deb9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FFCC863.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFFCC863.jpg&h=d4b7730d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Xp2AM8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Xp2AM8.jpg&h=e88c2844&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"967d1b4cfd0a1a440f3b8fedf4d617e678b6f575","tid":1326103,"uid":18012,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:50:35.000Z","msg":"師兄有冇pdf <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637c17d807a40fb6413c8381551be26dff8a0e95","tid":1326103,"uid":41145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:51:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c03edeebc96fcb548f6feb3a7b3b4d450d53924","tid":1326103,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"967d1b4cfd0a1a440f3b8fedf4d617e678b6f575","tid":1326103,"uid":18012,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-